nodes.text: A fleet group served within the Republic Navy's Open Circle Fleet that was under the command of Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi and Jedi General Anakin Skywalker during the Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems. The fleet group participated in the Battle of Yerbana, and then subsequently participated in the Battle of Coruscant. The fleet group consisted of five Venator-class Star Destroyers.
